metadata.name: Floki "The Phoenix"
metadata.description:
1.1 - Ex Icarus - Floki "The Phoenix"

The evacuation was led by the wise and just ruler, Floki, who had brought peace and prosperity to the land. But as the planet fell into its sun, a powerful and ambitious cyberpunk leader named Xander rose up against Floki, declaring himself the new ruler of Icarus.  The war between Floki and Xander and his forces, using the most advanced technology and weapons at their disposal, ravaged the planet for years. The final battle between Floki "The Phoenix" and Xander "The Shadow" was a clash of epic proportions. As the planet of Icarus hurtled towards its sun, the two warriors stood at the forefront of their respective armies, ready to determine the fate of their civilization.  
 Floki is the leader of the Icarans, a wise and just ruler who brought peace and prosperity to the land. He is the protagonist of the story, leading the evacuation of the planet Icarus as it falls into its sun. He fights against the ambitious general Xander, who attempts to seize power and become the ruler of Icarus. Floki ultimately emerges victorious, but at the cost of his civilization and home planet. He leads his people to the Phoenix Arks, where they begin anew as they journey through space. He is a strong and determined leader who cares deeply for his people and will do whatever it takes to protect them.


 Join the journey verifying this NFT in the Cyber Café discord and get access to the private Phoenix Ark Citizens with more insides about the story, characters, arts and the Ark community!
